0cm; text-indent: 0cm; &quot;>回车符</p></td></tr><tr><td width=&quot;280&quot; style=&quot;border-right-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-style: none solid solid none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 210.35pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; &quot;><p class=&quot;a0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 0cm; &quot;>/f</p></td><td width=&quot;281&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 210.4pt; border-style: none none solid; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; &quot;><p class=&quot;a0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 0cm; &quot;>走纸符</p></td></tr><tr><td width=&quot;280&quot; style=&quot;border-right-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-style: none solid solid none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 210.35pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; &quot;><p class=&quot;a0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 0cm; &quot;>/n</p></td><td width=&quot;281&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 210.4pt; border-style: none none solid; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; &quot;><p class=&quot;a0&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0cm; text-indent: 0cm; &quot;>换行符</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>换行符的作用是在下一行行首显示换行符后面的文本，请看下面的例子：</p><p class=&quot;a7&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>System.out.println(&quot;Music by/nMichael Nyman&quot;);</p><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>这条语句将显示如下内容：</p><p class=&quot;a7&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>Music by</p><p class=&quot;a7&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>Michael Nyman</p></div>', '13858769654127851457770822142537', '1386090678434', null, null);
INSERT INTO `notes` VALUES ('13860908089440612732810872529362', '2013，在路上', '', '<p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>到<a data-kw=&quot;伦敦&quot; href=&quot;http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/11124.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;link _j_keyword&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(77, 77, 77); border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px;&quot;>伦敦</a>求学已经三个月了，学习非常紧凑，一直没有时间到其他地方去玩。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>一放假第一站就选择了<a data-kw=&quot;牛津&quot; href=&quot;http://www.mafengwo.cn/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16162.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;link _j_keyword&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(77, 77, 77); border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; font-size: 14px;&quot;>牛津</a>。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>听很多朋友说牛津也没什么，半天就逛完了，走到后面还对那些建筑楼审美疲劳。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>可是我当天从上午10点左右到达牛津，到晚上7点离开，还是有些地方没去看，而且回来读了其他人的游记或是资料，才知道还有很多值得停留的地方只是匆匆走过。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>等到春夏鲜花开放绿草茵茵的时候，我要再去一次！</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>出发的前两天我在http://www.thetrainline.com订了火车票，这个网能订到比较便宜的火车票</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>由于我有16-25railcard,也就是大家常说的young person card，来回的火车票+订票费也只花了15磅</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>如果没有这张卡也没关系，来回票价是22磅左右。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>需要提醒大家的是，在决定哪一天去牛津之前最好先查查那里的学院是否开门，以及开放的时间段。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>如果不能进到学院参观，例如遇上放假，就比较可惜了</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>像我那天去Christ Church Colloge 基督教堂学院里的餐厅就不开放，那是《哈利波特》电影中他们吃饭的地点，没能进去太可惜了T T...</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>火车从Paddington出发，如果是在网上买从其他火车站出发的票，那则是用那张火车票先坐地铁到Paddington再上火车。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>火车大概是一小时多一点的路程。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>驶出伦敦市区后，沿路视野越来越开阔，看到的是广阔的平坦的草地，即使是寒冬腊月也还是绿色的。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>偶尔有几个小房子，不禁感叹能在那样的小房子里生活是多么休闲舒适~<br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>到了Oxford的火车站后到Informa台那张牛津地图就可以随意走了~</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>没有既定的最佳路线，在我看来，地图是帮助我知道自己眼前的建筑是什么而已，在牛津不存在迷路~</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>照片是火车站对面的公交站，后面的房子颜色是不是特别有英伦范儿？</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>这里的房子基本都是这样的高度<br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><a href=&quot;http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/16162/scenery_1090452/12498254.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 168, 0); border-bottom-width: 0px; cursor: pointer;&quot;><img src=&quot;http://file21.mafengwo.net/M00/61/D1/wKgB3FDZyimAQe6VAAxCYtrNTPA65.groupinfo.w600.jpeg&quot; title=&quot;牛津旅游攻略图片&quot; alt=&quot;牛津旅游攻略图片&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;391&quot; album_id=&quot;12498254&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block;&quot;></a></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 1