le=&quot;color: rgb(255, 168, 0); border-bottom-width: 0px; cursor: pointer;&quot;><img src=&quot;http://file20.mafengwo.net/M00/63/C6/wKgB3FDZzyWAXVvXADYdCK4SEvE66.groupinfo.w600.jpeg&quot; title=&quot;牛津自助游图片&quot; alt=&quot;牛津自助游图片&quot; width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;600&quot; album_id=&quot;12498291&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block;&quot;></a></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>圣坛旁有一扇圣凯萨琳之窗（St. Catherine&#039;s Window）的彩色玻璃窗，是把童话爱丽丝梦游仙境中爱丽丝的姊姊爱蒂丝（Edith Liddell）描绘成圣人，具体位置在左手边的墙上第5扇窗，仔细找找兔子先生~</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>每次去到教堂，总是觉得这些彩色的玻璃窗在阳光的透射下非常美丽壮观。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>这种由各色小块玻璃镶嵌的工艺是从阿拉伯国家学得的。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>一幅幅彩色的花窗成为不识字的教徒的圣经，起到宣传教义的作用。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>我并不是教徒，但是当阳光通过花窗照射进来，使得原本就能让人肃然起敬教堂，更添一份平静安详。<br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><a href=&quot;http://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/16162/scenery_1090452/12498292.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 168, 0); border-bottom-width: 0px; cursor: pointer;&quot;><img src=&quot;http://file21.mafengwo.net/M00/63/C7/wKgB3FDZzzuAbq9vAAjY_i1aZRM25.groupinfo.w600.jpeg&quot; title=&quot;牛津图片&quot; alt=&quot;牛津图片&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; height=&quot;401&quot; album_id=&quot;12498292&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block;&quot;></a></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>&nbsp;</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>游客对于圣经故事不太了解也没有关系，教堂里会有几位志愿者，如果你对里面某样装饰特别感兴趣，可以询问他们，他们会非常详细和耐心地讲解。</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>我在拍这个雕塑的时候一位志愿者老太太来问我是否了解这个雕塑的含义，我尴尬地说不知道</p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;>她说这只鸟因为找不到食物给自己的孩子，就撕自己身上的血肉喂食，老太太怕我听不明白，基本上是手舞足蹈加上各种声音模仿给我讲了好几个故事，非常热情！<br></p><p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-family: Arial, &#039;Microsoft Yahei&#039;, 微软雅黑, Tahoma, Helvetica, STHeiti, &#039;Hiragino Sans GB&#039;; line-height: 24px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px;&quot;><a href=&quot;htt